If $filter is not provided, no filtering is performed. If $filter=atExactScope() is provided, the returned list only includes all policy set definitions that at the given scope. If $filter='policyType -eq {value}' is provided, the returned list only includes all policy set definitions whose type match the {value}. Possible policyType values are NotSpecified, BuiltIn, Custom, and Static.
